                  </persName>
            . I was standing at the door when my brother-in-law brought the prisoner back - I saw him take the two packets of combs from under his apron, and put them back into the window.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was full two yards from the window when Bostock was buying the kite.</p>
